{"tid":560052,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"內部開發文件，iOS 12恐怕不會有太多讓你興奮的新功能","createTime":"2018-02-13T18:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T14:54:31.000Z","uid":10788,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2dfaf38f5a1159343bea3332a4a75636c96e5bc8","tid":560052,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T18:03:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/48168/apple-changes-ios-development-culture\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnext.com.tw%2Farticle%2F48168%2Fapple-changes-ios-development-culture&d=aauSO5M1qLMrxK%2FXnFuwezQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=aaa17aea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/48168/apple-changes-ios-development-culture</a>"},{"pid":"35460f9632c36147412d5484b36b18ab5bb4e52a","tid":560052,"uid":10788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T18:04:30.000Z","msg":"蘋果往年都固定在6月開發大會時，宣布新版iOS與macOS一堆新功能，然後在9月時釋出更新，讓所有用戶免費下載新系統，享用新功能。<br />\n<br />\n然而，每年為了趕這樣的日程，卻造成蘋果常在功能尚未穩定時就釋出更新，造成系統軟體出錯、問題頻頻。像是去年發生過的iPhone更新系統當機事件，就是系統品質未穩定所衍生的問題。<br />\n<br />\n現在，根據外媒Bloomberg報導，蘋果在上個月就默默地動大刀改了這個開發文化，為避免內部軟體部門在狂趕Deadline的情況下出紕漏，蘋果要讓工程師在確保軟體品質後，再釋出新功能給用戶。<br />\n<br />\n當然蘋果還是預計維持每年6月發表新系統的慣例，但是當年趕不上新功能開發完成的工程師，現在有權說自己尚未開發完成，把新功能延到隔年再推出。<br />\n<br />\nApple WWDC 2017<br />\n每年預計在6月全新改版作業系統的蘋果，傳大改內部開發流程，讓工程師能延遲上線尚未完成的功能。<br />\nApple<br />\n也因為這項變動，今年6月預計發表的iOS 12，似乎不會迎來太多全新功能。根據Bloomberg消息，iOS 12預計看到某些原生App的全新設計介面、新的「勿擾（Do Not Disturb）」功能，蘋果也預計把人臉動畫表情符號Animoji的功能帶到FaceTime上，但謠傳已久的新Home鍵設計，將因為開發成果尚未確切，再延後一年。<br />\n<br />\n其他洩出的蘋果消息還包括：新款iPad也將採納Face ID相機鏡頭，另外為了方便開發者，蘋果也在打造一個新的開發平台，讓iOS與macOS的App互通，讓開發者開發的App能直接在iPhone、iPad與Mac產品上使用（如微軟的Universal App一樣的概念）。"},{"pid":"8ad6c1c1b2ce5fbfe3ed8c99f8be92e3aaf3b30e","tid":560052,"uid":128210,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T18:09:51.000Z","msg":"其實都好正常者。<br />\n有咩可能年年有新野。<br />\n<br />\n7 同 8 都無咩新野。<br />\n係無左個3.5mm 插頭同多左個雙鏡頭。"},{"pid":"d940c0234a2d617f30044b4b4daf2c0694dbe812","tid":560052,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T18:26:37.000Z","msg":"好事ios11真係慘過食屎"},{"pid":"d16e10096456a42819575665a6317c6fe65b52f2","tid":560052,"uid":47239,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T23:28:02.000Z","msg":"Night mode呢？"},{"pid":"b2ab34a7339703892dff000ef45b427a557d0480","tid":560052,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T23:32:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老母又update<br />\n<br />\ngay cock 死全家"},{"pid":"6404bdbb49c1924977a733462136b1ac12bf52b6","tid":560052,"uid":65603,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T23:34:01.000Z","msg":"小d bugs已經好興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e534d7d106fde423840935da0d1b4cfe38c247b","tid":560052,"uid":51932,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T23:36:06.000Z","msg":"唔趕出貨，搞掂晒先出，係一件好事<br />\n<br />\niOS 11<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f505f82e61b4c04d3d0d38db53aaef2511152a","tid":560052,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2ab34a7339703892dff000ef45b427a557d0480","tid":560052,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T23:32:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老母又update<br />\n<br />\ngay cock 死全家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:08:16.000Z","msg":"科技一日千里"},{"pid":"4a879af31a56ab3cb46bf6504586762f96f30d75","tid":560052,"uid":137835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"你睇下人地android出得幾撚快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又係一年一代"},{"pid":"bd90c287a07a4273c318058fc7848ba7193b33e1","tid":560052,"uid":79180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a879af31a56ab3cb46bf6504586762f96f30d75","tid":560052,"uid":137835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite